---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Service Times">
  <h1>Service Times</h1>

  <p>Service Times is the weekly schedule shown on the public homepage and the dedicated /service-times page.</p>
  <h2>Fields per entry</h2>
  <p>Day of week, start time, end time (optional), name (e.g., "Sunday Morning Worship"), location (optional), description (optional).</p>
  <h2>Display order</h2>
  <p>Drag to reorder; the order on /admin/service-times reflects the order shown publicly.</p>
</BaseLayout>
